list.comment: metric_collector.py: - Fixed an issue that could've caused the get_similarity method to crash on string index out of range (assuming that the problem was in the HomoglyphsRatio method and in the slim chance that Elasticsearch would return a string instead of a JSON object.

Completed the first version of the metrics analyzer. It should now support receiving metrics (in graphite format) both in UDP and TCP and detect anomalies in the metrics data that is coming in.
